  "comment": "VELVET EVO 2: EVO 2 is a weatherproof panel with a 100% aluminum housing, designed specifically to endure the toughest working conditions in wet or dusty locations.\nIt delivers the same full output powered by two standard V-Lock or Gold Mount batteries as it does from AC power. EVO’s back panel has a twist-on plate to quickly install the battery mount, AC power supply, or center ball mount.\n\n \n\nVELVET CYC 3 color tunable articulated LED fixture includes:\n\nBuilt-in AC power supply to run exclusively AC from 90V to 264V\n\n3x horizontal light battens individually controlled\n\n2x XLR5 connectors (In and Through) for DMX-RDM wire control\n\nWi-Fi Art-Net wireless remote control\n\n\nThe VELVET CYC are compact, portable, silent, maintenance-free and high-quality color tunable LED cyclorama lights.\n\nThe VELVET CYC emit variable colored light with adjustable color temperature and adjustable green/magenta correction.\n\nEvery fixture can be controlled using DMX-RDM protocol, Art-Net through Wi-Fi or locally with shock-resistant buttons and color display.",
